Enum OperationTimeoutException.Operation

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<OperationTimeoutException.Operation>

    OperationTimeoutException

    public static enum OperationTimeoutException.Operation
extends java.lang.Enum<OperationTimeoutException.Operation>
    The operation on which the gatt layer encountered an error. Corresponds rough to all of the operations possible on a GattPeripheral object.

    • Enum Constant Summary
